Articles.Content: Finally made it to Duna, landed and back home safely. It's a great moment, and I'm very proud. That is all...

Well done!

(especially the getting back bit ~ my first attempt stranded three Kerbalnauts in an extended solar orbit.
Well done! Getting on Duna is hard for your first time.
Cheers guys! I had a fair amount of fuel left. Think I might make it to some of the outer planets with the same config! Minus the chutes for no atmosphere landers though.
